The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Sanath to play for Lancashire 

London: Sanath Jayasuriya is to join Lancashire on a short-term contract to cover for the absence of fellow spinner Muttiah Muralidharan. 

A statement from the English county on Wednesday said the 37-year old would replace Muralitharan (from June 19-July 20) while the off-spinner plays in Sri Lankas Test series against Bangladesh. 

